text: Jamar Shipman (born April 21, 1985 in Elizabeth, New Jersey) is an American professional wrestler who currently wrestles for All Elite Wrestling (AEW) and Ring of Honor (ROH) under the ring name, Jay Lethal. He is also known for wrestling for Total Nonstop Action Wrestling (TNA) from 2005 to 2011. ==Championships== Lethal has held many championships during his professional wrestling career: * American
